me.armar.plugins.autorank.language
Enum Lang

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<Lang>
      me.armar.plugins.autorank.language.Lang
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Lang>
public enum Lang
extends java.lang.Enum<Lang>

Every enumeration value has its path and default value. To get the path, do getPath(). To get the default value, do getDefault(). For the defined value in the lang.yml config, use getConfigValue(String[]). A string array is expected for the input. This can be null

Author:
Staartvin and gomeow
